ent","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r034-02.png","src":"/images/resident/r034-02.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"規劃匯總"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"規劃匯總"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"衛星公園的串接措施"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 樂捷段 147 地號"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提案者: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1GJzRbmWwx/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫議員"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n方案:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將樂捷段 147 號地, 設置為公 20 公園的附屬停車場及兒童遊戲區。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將樂學路的路邊停車遷移至上述公園附屬停車場。 讓樂學路能增加車道, 使得區域主要路線樂學路交通能夠順暢。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在樂善段 176 號地附近, 除了李宗豪議員的規劃, 雅倫注意到私有畸零地的垃圾對附近樂善國小及文德幼兒園的隱患！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫將要求市府用都市發展基金取得附近私有畸零地, 整理此區域為遊戲場及公園。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網友建議："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"微型共融遊戲空間"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 利用空間打造安全、低成本的迷你兒童遊戲設施（如搖搖馬、小型攀爬架、跳格子）。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 加值點：服務樂善國小低年級學童的放學空檔、家長接送等候時間"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 優點：不需大規模開發，社區共照友善"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"eleme